  "body": "While improving the performance of the emoji picker an issue was found:\r\n\r\n## [IOS] Disappearing emojis when selecting a filter during scrolling in emoji drawer on iOS\r\n\r\n## Steps:\r\n\r\n 1. Open the emoji drawer.\r\n 2. Begin scrolling through the emojis.\r\n 3. While the emoji drawer is actively scrolled, tap on a filter option located below the emojis\r\n\r\nActual result:\r\n\r\nWhen scrolling through the emojis and simultaneously selecting a filter, the emojis disappear from view.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/a8b047c4-7cc6-4716-8224-feabdae2812b\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nThe emojis should remain displayed\r\n\r\n### Device:\r\niPhone 11 Pro max, IOS 16\r\n\r\nReported by @VolodLytvynenko \r\n\r\nAdditionally, the emoji picker is in a `context` namespace, it should be in a `common` one instead.",
